{"tid":580024,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"千奇咪撚用us cinema app！！","createTime":"2018-03-04T06:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T11:27:04.000Z","uid":3742,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb6143501e47a347ef1b586114ae50305163b1e5","tid":580024,"uid":3742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"我係現場見到棟個牌話入loyal club 120蚊即送2張飛<br />\n望真d原來一張係要生日先送 都算<br />\n佢積分換領個度 係完全show唔到野<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/142703_c7ccea4160b5594e025f9897718c061a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F142703_c7ccea4160b5594e025f9897718c061a.png&h=d32b5ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好啦都算 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/142757_05c2b629aed77b9566d45deaa6519a97.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F142757_05c2b629aed77b9566d45deaa6519a97.png&h=0b33ef56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用app買去到要我入信用卡no都未有地方比我用優惠券<br />\n而且上網買本身就貴20蚊<br />\n好啦到我即場用電子自助機買<br />\n又係無得比我用優惠券<br />\n屌你老母咩<br />\n然後望望 $105根本無9折到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/143223_a50600c3272e72067755ebb5243515ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F143223_a50600c3272e72067755ebb5243515ef.png&h=61df887b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入撚到個按此睇真d條款 星期2/早場/首場嘅戲先至有<br />\n結果比左120蚊做水魚<br />\nua食屎啦！！！"},{"pid":"ca9bcf25eea4f157aa916d56b90ffefa910b3cd7","tid":580024,"uid":3742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T06:37:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b9330c8d0b6e4a7d088bca4e8d7